images.name: CeeDee Lamb exits in the first quarter with an ankle injury
images.caption: Cowboys receiver CeeDee Lamb is ruled out of the game after being tackled awkwardly on a rush attempt.

articles.description: Cowboys receiver CeeDee Lamb twisted his left ankle on a carry in the first quarter Sunday at Chicago but is optimistic about playing next week. He will undergo an MRI on Monday, a source told ESPN.
articles.headline: Cowboys' CeeDee Lamb injures ankle in loss, will have MRI

articles.description: Cardinals running back James Conner suffered a season-ending right ankle injury during Sunday's loss to the 49ers, and he will require surgery, a source told ESPN.
articles.headline: Source: Cardinals' James Conner suffers season-ending ankle injury
